-- Gazprom, China Agree on ‘Parameters’ for Gas Supplies From 2015
-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 2010-09-22T12:07:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-22/gazprom-china-agree-on-parameters-for-gas-supplies-from-2015.html
OAO Gazprom  agreed on the
“parameters” for natural-gas supplies to China that may start
in 2015, the Moscow-based gas company said today in an e-mailed
statement, without providing details.  Gazprom and  China National Petroleum Corp . plan to sign at
the end of this month an expanded accord on supply terms, which
will serve as a basis for a future contract, Deputy Chief
Executive Officer  Alexander Medvedev  said in the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Bierman in Moscow at 
